anime_data = [['Romance', '青春ブタ野郎', 'Rascal Does Not Dream', '2019', '5', 'Puberty syndrome -- Abnormal experiences rumored on the internet to be caused by sensitivity and instability during adolescence. This year, Sakuta Azusagawa, a second-year student at a high school near Enoshima, meets several girls that are experiencing this “puberty syndrome.” For instance, he meets a wild bunny girl in the library. She turns out to be an actress on hiatus, Mai Sakurajima, who is also his senior at the school. For some reason, no one else can see this enchanting girl. How did she become invisible…?']
              ['Romance', '五等分の花嫁', 'The Quintessential Quintuplets', '2019', '5', "Uesugi Fuutarou, a high school second-year from a poor family, receives a highly appealing offer to work part-time as a tutor... but his students turn out to be girls from his own class! What's more, they're quintuplets... and all five are beautiful, but happen to be problem students who have borderline grades and hate studying! Looks like his first assignment will be to win all the sisters' trust?! Every day is a wild party in this rom-com centering around the quintuplet sisters of the Nakano household!"]
              ['Romance', 'やはり俺の青春ラブコメはまちがっている。', 'My Teen Romantic Comedy SNAFU', '2013', '5', "So exactly what's going to happen when Hachiman Hikigaya, an isolated high school student with no friends, no interest in making any and a belief that everyone else's supposedly great high school experiences are either delusions or outright lies, is coerced by a well meaning faculty member into joining the one member “Services Club” run by Yukino Yukinoshita, who's smart, attractive and generally considers everyone in her school to be her complete inferior?"]
              ['Sci-fi', 'シュタインズ・ゲート', 'Steins;Gate 0', '2011', '5', 'A divergent continuation of the original Steins;Gate ending, Steins;Gate 0 explores an alternate worldline where Okabe abandons time travel. While attempting to forget past traumas and get his life back on track, he meets an AI that re-opens old wounds.']
              ['Fantasy', '凪のあすから', 'Nagi no Asukara', '2013', '4.5', 'Long ago, all humans lived in the ocean. But some who longed for the land abandoned the ocean, casting off the special raiments granted to them by the sea god to adapt them to life under the sea...']
              ['Freindship', 'あの日見た花の名前を僕達はまだ知らない。', 'Anohana: The Flower We Saw That Day', '2011', '4.5', 'Jinta Yadomi and his group of childhood friends have become estranged after a tragic accident split them apart. Now in their high school years, a sudden surprise forces each of them to confront their guilt over what happened that day and come to terms with the ghosts of their past.']
              ['Romance', 'かぐや様は告らせたい 〜天才たちの恋愛頭脳戦〜', 'Kaguya-sama: Love Is War', '2019', '5', "From a good family? Check! A good personality? Check!\nShuchiin Academy is where all these elite students with bright futures flock to.\nAs the two leaders of the student council, Kaguya Shinomiya and Miyuki Shirogane have supposedly fallen in love…\nBut after almost half a year, nothing has happened!?\nThey both have too much pride and can't be honest.\nThings have gotten troublesome, and they are now caught in a war of 'How to get the other to confess their love first.'\n\nThis is a whole new romantic comedy, following an outbreak of cunning warfare between two elite students in love."]
              ['Romance', '冴えない彼女の育てかた', 'Saekano: How to Raise a Boring Girlfriend', '2015', '4.5', "Tomoya Aki, an otaku high school student, has a dream of creating his own visual novel. With his friends' help, he recruits several girls, including the popular Eriri Spencer Sawamura, to become the game's character designers. As they learn more about each other, Tomoya realizes that he is actually in love with one of the girls and sets out to make his game and confess his feelings to her."]
              ['Supernatural', 'サマータイムレンダ', 'Summer Time Rendering', '2021', '4.5', 'When a group of friends reunite after a decade-long hiatus, strange things start happening on their summer vacation, leading them to investigate the cause of the supernatural events.']
              ['Romance', '四月は君の嘘', 'Your Lie in April', '2014', '4', 'A talented young pianist who lost the ability to hear the sound of his own playing after the death of his abusive mother meets a free-spirited violinist who helps him rediscover his love for music.']
              ['Romance', 'ひげを剃る。そして女子高生を拾う。', 'Higehiro: After Being Rejected, I Shaved and Took in a High School Runaway', '2021', '4', 'After his beloved wife passes away, a salaryman finds solace in drinking and neglects his work and home responsibilities. One day, he encounters a high school girl who is sleeping on the street and takes her in, and the two gradually form a bond.']
              ['Romance', '神様になった日', 'The Day I Became a God', '2020', '3.5', 'The story follows a young girl named Hina who suddenly awakens as a god and is told that the world will end in 30 days. She chooses a boy named Youta to spend the remaining time with, and the two travel around the world, seeking to fulfill their wishes before the end of the world.']
              ['Romance', 'さくら荘のペットな彼女', 'The Pet Girl of Sakurasou', '2012', '4', 'The story follows Sorata Kanda, a high school sophomore who is living in Sakurasou, the dormitory for problem students at his school. When Mashiro Shiina, a world-famous artist, transfers to the school and moves into Sakurasou, Sorata is assigned to take care of her. The series follows Sorata and the other residents of Sakurasou as they pursue their dreams and face the challenges of growing up.']
              ['Romance', '月がきれい', 'Tsuki ga Kirei', '2017', '4', 'The story follows the relationship between two middle school students, Kotarou Azumi and Akane Mizuno, as they struggle to balance their feelings for each other with the pressures of school and their families. The series explores the ups and downs of first love and the challenges of growing up.']
              ['Thiller', 'ようこそ実力至上主義の教室へ', 'Classroom of the Elite', '2017', '4.5', "Ayanokouji Kiyotaka is a student of D-class, which is where the school dumps its 'inferior' students in order to ridicule them. For a certain reason, Kiyotaka was careless on his entrance examination, and was put in D-class. After meeting Horikita Suzune and Kushida Kikyou, two other students in his class, Kiyotaka's situation begins to change."]
              ['Action', '86―エイティシックス―', '86 Eighty-Six', '2021', '4.5', "The Republic of San Magnolia has been at war with the neighboring Giadian Empire for years. In order to fight the drones of the Empire, the Republic has been using the 'Legion' system, which consists of unmanned drones being controlled by the 'Handlers' from the safety of the rear. However, there are those who cannot accept this situation -- the '86ers,' named so because they are not considered to be fully human. This is their story."]
              ['Thiller', 'シャドーハウス', 'Shadows House', '2021', '4', 'The Shadows are a family of living dolls that serve as the faceless retainers of a wealthy household. Every day, they dutifully go about their tasks, their expressions never changing, but the arrival of a new living doll named Emilico throws their lives into chaos.']
              ['Comedy', 'ぐらんぶる', 'Grand Blue', '2018', '4', 'Iori Kitahara moves to the coastal town of Izu for his freshman year at university and quickly finds himself drawn into the wild and boozy world of the local diving club.']
              ['Sports', '賭ケグルイ', 'Kakegurui - Compulsive Gambler', '2017', '4', 'At Hyakkaou Private Academy, the students are ranked by their gambling winnings, and a class system is in place. However, transfer student Jabami Yumeko shakes things up with her love of high-stakes gambling.']
              ['Thiller', '僕だけがいない街', 'ERASED', '2016', '4.5', 'Satoru Fujinuma is a young manga artist struggling to make a name for himself following his debut. But, that was not the only thing in his life that Satoru was feeling frustrated about…he was also living with a strange condition only he was able to experience.\n\n- REVIVAL\nA strange phenomenon where one is transferred back to the moment right before something life-threatening occurs. This continues to happen until the cause of the threat is erased. It is as if somebody is forcing Satoru to stop it from happening.']
              ['Thiller', 'オッドタクシー', 'Odd Taxi', '2021', '4.5', 'A story about the lives of various animals in a city, including a taxi driver who becomes embroiled in a mystery.']
              ['Fantasy', '宝石の国', 'Land of the Lustrous', '2017', '3.5', 'In a world where gems are living beings, a group of them must defend themselves from attackers who seek to use them for their power.']
              ['Thiller', '残響のテロル', 'Terror in Resonance', '2014', '4', '"In an alternate version of the present, Tokyo has been hit by a terrorist attack that has devastated the city. The only evidence of the culprits is a cryptic video uploaded to the internet, which sparks paranoia across Japan. Six months later, a young man named Nine and his accomplice Twelve, who are part of a counter-terrorism unit composed of only two people, steal plutonium from a nuclear fuel cycle facility in nuclear reprocessing plant in Aomori. The two terrorists promise Tokyo that they will detonate the plutonium if their demands are not met. The two terrorists then use a nuclear bomb to destroy an empty skyscraper in Tokyo. Nine leaves a message telling the authorities that the bomb was only a warning. The police then realize that the terrorists are among the students of a local high school, leading to a cat-and-mouse game between the police and the terrorists."']
              ['Sci-Fi', '新世紀エヴァンゲリオン', 'Neon Genesis Evangelion', '1995', '3.5', "A group of teenagers pilot giant robots to defend against mysterious beings known as 'angels.'"]
              ['Supernatural', '虚構推理', 'In/Spectre', '2020', '3', "In/Spectre follows the story of Kotoko Iwanaga, a girl who was kidnapped by the yokai and asked to become their 'God of Wisdom,' a mediator between the spirit and human worlds, to which she agreed. With her newfound powers, she helps the police solve cases involving the supernatural."]
              ['Romance', 'ニセコイ', 'Nisekoi', '2014', '3.5', 'Raku Ichijou, a first-year student at Bonyari High School, is the sole heir to an intimidating yakuza family. Ten years ago, Raku made a promise to his childhood friend. Now, all he has to go on is a pendant with a lock, which can only be unlocked with the key which the girl took with her when they parted.']
              ['Romance', '彼女、お借りします', 'Rent-a-Girlfriend', '2020', '3.5', 'Kazuya Kinoshita is dumped by his girlfriend after dating for only a month. He decides to use a matchmaking app to rent a girlfriend named Chizuru Mizuhara, but things start to get complicated when they begin to develop real feelings for each other.']
              ['Romance', '可愛いだけじゃない式守さん', "Shikimori's Not Just a Cutie", '2021', '3.5', 'The ultimate \'heartthrob girlfriend\' appears! Naturally unlucky high school student Izumi\'s girlfriend is his classmate Shikimori. She has a beautiful smile and kind personality and always seems happy when she\'s with Izumi. She\'s a pretty, cute, and loving girlfriend, but when Izumi\'s in trouble... she transforms into a super cool "heartthrob girlfriend!" The fun lives of the cute and cool Shikimori, Izumi, and their good friends never end! This 1000% precious romantic comedy begins now!']
              ['Romance', 'トニカクカワイイ', 'TONIKAWA: Over The Moon For You', '2020', '3.5', 'Nasa Yuzaki falls in love at first sight after an encounter with the mysterious Tsukasa. When Nasa earnestly confesses his feelings, she replies, "I\'ll date you, but only if we\'re married." Nasa and Tsukasa\'s cute and precious newlywed life of love is about to begin!']
              ['Romance', 'ホリミヤ', 'Horimiya', '2021', '3.5', 'When the popular Hori and the gloomy Miyamura meet, they reveal another side of themselves. Could this be the start of something new?']
              ['Action', 'エンジェルビーツ', 'Angel Beats!', '2010', '3.5', 'Otonashi is a young boy living in the afterlife with no memories of his life before his death. He joins a school organization called the SSS whose mission is to fight against God.']
              ['School', '氷菓', 'Hyouka', '2012', '3.5', "Hyouka is a stunning masterwork that spins a charming tale of high school romance and mystery. After disenchanted student Hotaro Oreki joins his school's Classic Lit Club, he meets Eru Chitanda, a kindhearted and inquisitive girl with boundless curiosity and a knack for getting him caught up in all sorts of trouble."]
              ['Fantasy', 'シャーロット', 'Charlotte', '2015', '3.5', 'Very few adolescent boys and girls have an onset of special abilities. Yu Otosaka is one such man who uses his ability unbeknownst to others in order to lead a satisfying school life. Then one day, a girl named Nao Tomori suddenly appears before him. Their encounter reveals the destiny for wielders of special abilities.']
              ['Romance', '継母の連れ子が元カノだった', "My Stepmom's Daughter Is My Ex", '2021', '3.5', 'A boy and a girl started dating in middle school. They were lovey-dovey at first, but due to a misunderstanding over something trivial, they started feeling more frustration than excitement... In the end, they broke up when they graduated. However, Mizuto Irido and Yume Ayai meet again in a surprising way before they start high school. "Obviously I\'m the older brother here." "Obviously I\'m the older sister here." The child of their parent\'s new spouse is the ex they just broke up with?! Out of consideration for their parents, this former couple comes up with a "sibling rule," which is: "Whoever starts seeing the other as potentially attractive loses." But they sometimes run into each other right after a bath. They\'re also alone on their way to and from school, so... Because of the memories they share and because of this situation where they live under the same roof, how can they help but pay attention to each other?!']
              ['Romance', '恋と嘘', 'Love and Lies', '2017', '3.5', 'In a futuristic society, Japan has implemented a complex system referred to as "The Red Threads of Science" to encourage successful marriages and combat increasingly low birthrates. Based on a compatibility calculation, young people at the age of 16 are assigned marriage partners by the government, with severe repercussions awaiting those who disobey the arrangement.For Yukari Nejima, a teen that considers himself average in every way, this system might be his best shot at living a fulfilling life.']
              ['Romance', '俺の妹がこんなに可愛いわけがない', 'Oreimo', '2010', '3', "Kyosuke Kosaka, a normal 17-year-old high school student living in Chiba, has not gotten along with his younger sister Kirino in years. For longer than he can remember, Kirino has ignored his comings and goings and looked at him with spurning eyes. It seemed as if the relationship between Kyōsuke and his sister, now fourteen, would continue this way forever. One day however, Kyosuke finds a DVD case of a magical girl anime which had fallen in his house's entrance way."]
              ['Romance', '色づく世界の明日から', 'Iroduku: The World in Colors', '2018', '3', "Despite the kaleidoscopic magic ingrained in everyday life, Hitomi Tsukishiro's monochrome world is deprived of emotion and feeling. On a night as black and white as any other, amidst the fireworks spreading across the sky, Hitomi's grandmother Kohaku conjures a spell, for which she has been harnessing the moon's light for 60 years, to send Hitomi back in time to the year 2018 when Kohaku was in high school."]
              ['Friendship', '僕は友達が少ない', "Haganai: I Don't Have Many Friends", '2011', '3', 'Yozora and Kodoka are social catastrophes at their school. In order to make friends with other misfits, they start the Neighbors Club. In no time, a third member joins the club: Sena, a popular girl who annoys Yozora to no end. If the girls can get past their rivalry, they might learn an important lesson: Sometimes the best friends are the friends you never even wanted.']
              ['Action', 'リコリス・リコイル', 'Lycoris Recoil', '2020', '3.5', 'In the year 2037, a neural network linking all of humanity, "The Wired", is born. Lain, a quiet and reserved fourteen-year-old girl, finds herself caught up in a series of strange events regarding the network, leading to her discovery of just what The Wired is, and how it can affect society.']
              ['Supernatural', 'モブサイコ100', 'Mob Psycho 100', '2016', '4', 'Kageyama Shigeo (a.k.a. "Mob") is a 8th grader with psychic abilities. Since he was young, he has suppressed his powers, causing them to build up inside him. Now, the only thing he wants is to become friends with a girl in his class, Tsubomi. With his psychic "mentor" (who has no psychic powers), he continues his daily life, attempting to realize his purpose in life.']
              ['Music', 'ぼっち・ざ・ろっく！', 'Bocchi the Rock!', '2021', '4.5', 'Bocchi Hitori is a shy and withdrawn girl who struggles to make friends. After a chance encounter with a rock band, she decides to start her own band in hopes of making new friends.']
              ['Romance', '夫婦以上、恋人未満', 'More Than a Married Couple, But Not Lovers', '2022', '3.5', 'Towa and Mikado have been best friends since childhood, and after Towa confesses her love to Mikado, they begin a romantic relationship that is more than friendship, but not quite lovers.']
              ['Romance', '最近雇ったメイドが怪しい', 'The Maid I Hired Recently Is Mysterious', '2021', '3', 'When a young man hires a maid to take care of his household, he discovers that she has some mysterious and unusual habits.']
              ['Fantasy', '乙女ゲー世界はモブに厳しい世界です', 'Trapped in a Dating Sim: The World of Otome Games Is Tough for Mobs', '2021', '3', 'Leon, an ordinary office worker, suddenly finds himself transported into the world of his favorite otome game, a dating sim for girls. He is reincarnated as a minor character and quickly realizes that his life in this world will be very difficult as a "mob", a background character with no significant role.']
              ['Romance', 'カッコウの許嫁', 'A Couple of Cuckoos', '2021', '3.5', 'A romantic comedy about a boy named Nagi who falls in love at first sight with a girl named Erika. After confessing his feelings and being rejected, he discovers that Erika is actually his new neighbor and they end up attending the same high school.']
              ['Action', '忍の一時', "A Ninja's Moment", '2022', '2.5', 'A young man named Yae Asakura becomes a ninja in modern-day Japan and must balance his ninja training with his everyday life.']
              ['Slice of life', '明日ちゃんのセーラー服', "Akebi's Sailor Uniform", '2021', '4', 'A story about a girl named Akebi Komichi who transfers to a new school and starts a new life wearing a sailor uniform.']
              ['Romance', '死神坊ちゃんと黒メイドさん', 'The Duke of Death and His Maid', '2021', '3', 'A romantic comedy about a Duke cursed to bring death to everything he touches and his loyal maid who will do anything to lift the curse.']
              ['Fantasy', '異世界おじさん', 'Uncle from Another World', '2021', '3.5', 'A middle-aged man named Takafumi awakens in a fantasy world and uses his knowledge of modern technology to solve problems and help those in need.']
              ['Sports', 'ダイヤのA', 'Ace of Diamond', '2013', '5', "Eijun Sawamura is a pitcher who joins an elite school with a brilliant catcher named Kazuya Miyuki. Together with the rest of the team, they strive for Japan's storied Koushien championships through hard work and determination."]
              ['Sports', 'メジャー', 'MAJOR', '2004', '4', "Gorou Honda, a little boy obsessed with baseball, has always admired his father, Shigeharu. Wishing to follow in his father's footsteps, Gorou dreams of becoming a professional baseball player. In turn, his son's starry-eyed admiration encourages Shigeharu to keep persevering, despite his late wife's death and his unsatisfying position on the second-string team Blue Ocean.\n\nUnfortunately, an elbow injury forces Shigeharu off the team, and he falls into despair. However, after an offhand joke from his childhood friend, Shigeharu reevaluates his choices and decides to keep playing, leaving behind his prime position as pitcher and taking up the bat. Now motivated more than ever, Gorou works hard to carve his way in the Japanese Little League."]
              ['Sports', 'スラムダンク', 'SLAM DUNK', '1993', '5', 'Hanamichi Sakuragi, a tall and muscular delinquent, joins the basketball team of his school in order to impress a girl. Despite his initial disdain for the sport, he soon discovers a passion for it.']
              ['Sports', '黒子のバスケ', 'The Basketball which Kuroko Plays', '2012', '3.5', 'The Teiko Middle School Basketball Team: The class that produced three perfect seasons in a row, with five once-in-a generation players, called "The Generation of Miracles." There was another player who all of them respected... A legendary 6th player. An up-and-coming power player, Taiga Kagami, is just back from America. When he comes to Seirin High School, he meets the super-ordinary boy, Tetsuya Kuroko.']
              ['Adventure', '鋼の錬金術師 FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST', 'Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood', '2009', '5', 'The story follows two brothers, Edward and Alphonse Elric, who learn alchemy in order to bring back their deceased mother. After a terrible miscalculation, however, they pay a heavy price to set things right.']
              ['Sports', 'あひるの空', 'Ahiru no Sora', '2019', '3', "He may be shorter in stature, but Sora Kurumatani can soar and score on the basketball court! With a passion for the sport he inherited from his mother, Sora vows to her that he'll take top prize at a high school basketball tournament… but there's one problem. His new school's basketball club has turned into a hangout for delinquents! Will Sora's sheer tenacity and amazing three-point shooting change their minds and get the club up and running again?"]
              ['Adventure', 'ワンピース', 'One Piece', '1999', '4.5', 'Monkey D. Luffy sets out to become the King of the Pirates and find the One Piece treasure.']
              ['Adventure', 'ナルト', 'Naruto', '2002', '4.5', 'Naruto Uzumaki, a mischievous adolescent ninja, dreams of becoming the Hokage, the leader of his village.']
              ['Adventure', 'ブリーチ', 'Bleach', '2004', '3.5', 'Ichigo Kurosaki, a teenager with the ability to see ghosts, becomes a Soul Reaper and fights against evil spirits known as Hollows.']
              ['Adventure', 'ドラゴンボール', 'Dragon Ball', '1986', '4.5', 'Dragon Ball follows the adventures of Goku, a young martial artist who has a passion for the Dragon Balls, which when gathered together can grant any wish. Along with his friends and allies, Goku fights against a variety of villains to protect the Earth and its inhabitants.']
              ['Thiller', '名探偵コナン', 'Detective Conan', '1996', '5', 'Shinichi Kudo, a high school detective, is transformed into a child after being poisoned, and solves crimes while hiding his true identity.']
              ['Action', '進撃の巨人', 'Attack on Titan', '2013', '5', 'Eren Yeager and his friends fight against the Titans, giant humanoid creatures who devour humans without reason, in a world where humanity lives inside cities surrounded by enormous walls.']
              ['Adventure', '鬼滅の刃', 'Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba', '2019', '4', 'Tanjiro Kamado, a young man whose family was killed by demons, becomes a demon hunter in order to find a way to turn his sister back into a human.']
              ['Supernatural', '呪術廻戦', 'Jujutsu Kaisen', '2020', '4.5', 'Yuji Itadori, a high school student with incredible physical abilities, becomes a Jujutsu sorcerer and fights against cursed spirits to save the world.']
              ['Action', 'チェンソーマン', 'Chainsaw Man', '2021', '4', 'Denji is a young man living in a world overrun by devils who sell their body parts to humans for consumption in exchange for granting them special abilities. After being betrayed by his father-figure and struggling to make ends meet, Denji agrees to merge with his pet devil Pochita to become a devil hunter in exchange for money. But the devil hunter life is not as easy as it seems.']
              ['Action', '僕のヒーローアカデミア', 'My Hero Academia', '2016', '4.5', 'In a world where almost everyone has a superhuman ability, Izuku Midoriya is born without one. Despite this setback, he dreams of becoming a hero and enrolls in a high school for professional heroes. With the help of his idol, the legendary hero All Might, Izuku works hard to become a hero himself and protect the world from villains who threaten the peace.']
              ['Adventure', 'ヴィンランド・サガ', 'Vinland Saga', '2019', '4', 'Thorfinn is a young Viking warrior who seeks revenge against the man who killed his father, the mercenary leader Askeladd. Along the way, Thorfinn becomes embroiled in a larger conflict between the Danish and English armies, and must decide whether to follow his desire for revenge or his own sense of honor and justice.']
              ['Sports', 'ブルーロック', 'Blue Lock', '2021', '4', 'Yoichi Isagi is a talented soccer player who has been scouted by many top-level clubs. But when he is selected to participate in the Blue Lock project, a special training program designed to create the ultimate striker for the Japanese national team, Yoichi finds himself in a cutthroat competition against other talented players who will do anything to win.']
              ['Sci-Fi', 'ドクターストーン', 'Dr. Stone', '2019', '4', 'Thousands of years after a mysterious event turned all of humanity into stone, a high school student named Taiju awakens to find that the world has been restored to its pre-stone age state by a fellow student named Senku. Together, Taiju and Senku set out to rebuild civilization from scratch, using science and technology to overcome the challenges of a world that has been reset to zero.']
              ['Sports', 'アオアシ', 'Aoashi', '2021', '3.5', 'After experiencing defeat in the All-Japan High School Soccer Tournament, Seigo Narazaki decides to join one of the strongest high school soccer teams in Japan to improve his skills.']
              ['Comedy', 'スパイファミリー', 'Spy x Family', '2020', '4.5', 'In order to carry out his latest mission, a spy must create a fake family and enroll his daughter into an elite school for future world leaders, but things get complicated when his fake wife is actually an assassin and his daughter is a powerful telepath.']
              ['Adventure', 'ブラッククローバー', 'Black Clover', '2017', '4', 'In a world where magic is everything, Asta and Yuno are two orphans who dream of becoming the Wizard King, but while Yuno possesses exceptional magical powers, Asta has none, and must rely on his physical strength and unwavering determination to achieve his goal.']
              ['Thiller', '東京喰種-トーキョーグール-', 'Tokyo Ghoul', '2014', '4.5', 'After being transformed into a half-ghoul, Ken Kaneki must navigate between the two worlds of humans and ghouls, while trying to uncover the truth behind his transformation and survive in a society that fears and hates his kind.']
              ['Adventure', 'ハンター×ハンター', 'Hunter x Hunter', '1999', '5', 'Gon Freecss embarks on a journey to become a Hunter, a skilled warrior and explorer who hunts down rare and exotic creatures, in order to find his father and uncover the mysteries of his past.']
              ['Sports', 'ハイキュー!!', 'Haikyu!!', '2014', '4', "Shoyo Hinata dreams of becoming a great volleyball player despite his small stature, and joins his high school's volleyball team where he meets the talented setter Tobio Kageyama, with whom he forms an unlikely and powerful partnership."]
              ['Adventure', 'ジョジョの奇妙な冒険', "Jojo's Bizarre Adventure", '2012', '4', 'The Joestar family, who are possessed with unique powers, find themselves in danger when an evil vampire seeks to destroy them and take over the world.']
              ['Fantasy', 'ソードアート・オンライン', 'Sword Art Online', '2012', '4', "In the year 2022, a new virtual reality MMORPG called Sword Art Online is released, but the players soon find themselves trapped inside the game and must fight their way to the top of the game's tower in order to escape."]
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士ガンダム 水星の魔女', 'Mobile Suit Gundam: The Witch from Mercury', '2022', '4', 'A.S. (Ad Stella) 122― An era when a multitude of corporations have entered space and built a huge economic system. A lone girl from the remote planet Mercury transfers to the Asticassia School of Technology, run by the Beneritt Group which dominates the mobile suit industry. Her name is Suletta Mercury. With a scarlet light burning in her pure heart, this girl walks step by step through a new world.']
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士きどうせんしガンダム 鉄血てっけつのオルフェンズ', 'Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans', '2015', '5', 'In the far future, humanity has colonized several planets and moons in the solar system. Amidst the waning authority of the ruling body known as the Gjallarhorn, a group of child soldiers called the Tekkadan struggle to survive in a harsh world of corruption and violence.']
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士ガンダムSEED DESTINY', 'Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny', '2004', '3', "C.E. 73: While the second battle of Yachin Due brought the war between the Naturals and Coordinators to a close, tensions between the two races are at an all-time high. During a meeting between PLANT Chairman Gilbert Dullindal and Orb Representative Cagalli Yula Athha, a unit of soldiers from the Earth Alliance attacks the ZAFT base they're meeting at and makes off with three new Gundam mobile suits. Forced to pursue them, Shinn Asuka of ZAFT and Athrun Zala of Orb set out aboard the new battleship Minerva, and engage the Earth Forces' special-forces unit known as Phantom Pain."]
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士ガンダムSEED', 'Mobile Suit Gundam SEED', '2002', '3.5', 'In the midst of war between the Naturals (OMNI) and Coordinators (ZAFT), a young Coordinator named Kira Yamato pilots the Strike Gundam and is forced to fight his old friend Athrun Zala. Little do they know that there are sinister forces at work that threaten both of their existences.']
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士ガンダム00', 'Mobile Suit Gundam 00', '2007', '4', 'In the distant future, humanity has united to form the A-Laws, a new global government that seeks to eliminate war and conflict through force. However, a group of rebels known as Celestial Being emerges, wielding powerful Mobile Suits called Gundams that they use to intervene in conflicts around the world.']
              ['Sci-Fi', '新機動戦記ガンダムW', 'Mobile Suit Gundam Wing', '1995', '3.5', 'The series is set in the "After Colony" timeline, where a group of young pilots is recruited to fight in a war between Earth and its space colonies.']
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士ガンダム 閃光のハサウェイ', 'Mobile Suit Gundam Hathaway', '2021', '4', 'The story takes place in the year UC 0105 and follows Hathaway Noa, son of the late Bright Noa, as he joins a terrorist group fighting against the Earth Federation.']
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士ガンダムUC', 'Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn', '2010', '4', "Set in the year UC 0096, the story follows Banagher Links, a young student who becomes embroiled in a conflict between the Earth Federation and a rebel group known as the Sleeves over a mysterious object known as Laplace's Box."]
              ['Sci-Fi', '機動戦士ガンダムTHE ORIGIN', 'Mobile Suit Gundam: The Origin', '2015', '4.5', 'The series serves as a retelling of the original Mobile Suit Gundam series, with a focus on the backstory of key characters like Char Aznable and Sayla Mass.']
              ['Sports', '頭文字D', 'Initial D', '1998', '4', 'Takumi Fujiwara is an average 18-year-old high school student with an extraordinary talent for driving. He works at a gas station with his friend Itsuki, who also has a fondness for cars. The two soon discover that Takumi has a natural talent for drifting, which they realize when Takumi drives a girl named Natsuki home in her car, and they race on the twisty, mountain roads of Mount Akina. From that point on, Takumi slowly begins to develop his driving skills and hones his ability to drift.']
              ['Supernatural', 'デスノート', 'Death Note', '2006', '4.5', 'Light Yagami is an extremely intelligent young man who resents what appears to be a relentless increase in crime and corruption in the world around him. His life undergoes a drastic change when he discovers a mysterious notebook known as the Death Note, lying on the ground in the year 2003. With the Death Note, Light can kill anyone whose name he writes in it.']
              ['Action', 'キングダム', 'Kingdom', '2012', '4.5', 'Shin is a young orphan who dreams of becoming a general and leading the people of his village to glory. However, he has no special talent or skill, and is mocked and ostracized by the other children. One day, he meets a boy named Hyou who claims to be a slave who ran away from his master. Hyou teaches Shin how to fight and persuades him to join a quest to become great generals of the world.']
              ['Comedy', '銀魂', 'Gintama', '2006', '4.5', "In the world of the samurai, the skilled swordsmen known as the Shinsengumi are feared and respected for their ability to fight against the forces of evil. But when aliens invade the land and bring with them advanced technology and a new way of life, the samurai are left behind in a world they no longer understand. That's where Gintoki Sakata comes in - a samurai who has fallen on hard times, Gintoki now works as a jack-of-all-trades, taking on odd jobs and occasionally fighting to protect the people of Edo from danger."]
              ['Adventure', '犬夜叉', 'Inuyasha', '2000', '3.5', "Kagome Higurashi is a modern-day high school student who is transported to feudal Japan through a well in her family's shrine. There, she meets Inuyasha, a half-demon who seeks the Shikon Jewel to become a full demon. Together with the help of their friends, they embark on a journey to find the shards of the Shikon Jewel before it falls into the wrong hands."]
              ['Sci-Fi', 'コードギアス 反逆のルルーシュ', 'Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion', '2006', '4', "In an alternate world, the powerful Holy Britannian Empire conquers and enslaves many countries. In the conquered Japan, Lelouch Lamperouge, a young Britannian student, receives a power known as Geass, which allows him to control others' actions. Using his new abilities, Lelouch leads a rebellion against the Britannian Empire."]
              ['Adventure', 'メイドインアビス', 'Made in Abyss', '2017', '4', "In a world of mystery and peril, a young girl named Riko and her humanoid robot friend Reg descend into the depths of the Abyss, a massive network of caves that may hold the key to Riko's missing mother and incredible ancient treasures. Along the way, they encounter strange creatures and deadly traps, testing their strength and resolve as they venture deeper into the abyss."]
              ]

